aur2ccr - 
	Pull Arch packages from AUR or source files from Arch repos,
	and make source packages that are ready for uploading to CCR.

Todo: 	add the ability to grab packages from Arch repos; 
	add ability to search for packages in AUR as well as Arch repos;
	add signal handling with bash traps;
	add option to specify the URL of an AUR/CCR-compat source package to convert to CCR;
	add the ability to automatically upload packages to CCR (if possible);

This script uses the information on converting Arch/AUR packages to CCR source packages from 
http://chakra-linux.org/wiki/index.php/How_to_upload_a_package_to_CCR_when_it_exists_on_Arch_or_Aur
